{"type":"message","id":"7f7b9b7a","parentId":"c45dd458","timestamp":"2026-04-08T01:00:00.220Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:f61eec2a-69ea-4fd2-84b7-3d424eaaa653 每日推送claudecode最热动态] 请帮我获取最新claudecode相关的最热动态，包括github热门项目、最新工具发布、相关新闻资讯，整理成清晰的内容推送给用户ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 8th, 2026 — 9:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-08 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775610000212}}
{"type":"message","id":"bebb7be3","parentId":"7f7b9b7a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T01:00:05.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job to get the latest ClaudeCode-related hot trends and push them to the user. Let me search for the latest ClaudeCode news, GitHub trending projects, and related tools.\n\nLet me search for the latest information about ClaudeCode.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uzwgq9lelkyg_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":28225,"output":91,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28316,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775610000216}}
{"type":"message","id":"52a17fce","parentId":"bebb7be3","timestamp":"2026-04-08T01:00:05.598Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uzwgq9lelkyg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775610005583}}
{"type":"message","id":"3232a8f3","parentId":"52a17fce","timestamp":"2026-04-08T01:00:09.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for the latest ClaudeCode-related news, trending projects, and tools. I'll make multiple searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_omrv2b7xwsfx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ClaudeCode GitHub trending 2026\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_omrv2b7xwsfx_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ClaudeCode 最新资讯 2026年4月\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_omrv2b7xwsfx_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"Claude Code tools extensions 2026\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":612,"output":156,"cacheRead":28219,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775610005596}}
